# Welcome to Bos Development
 I don't create new staff but I just learn for fun.
 It is a new world. 
 There is no limitation for development except this repository is used to develop target OS on x86 machine.
 If you have any suggestion, please let me know.
tagline: A self-made Operation System in X86, Just fun for Learning
